Sentence: Forty - nine SD rats were grouped into seven groups comprising a reference group ( n = 7) fed a regular ( low - fat) chow, a group of AIA rats treated with vehicle ( n = 7), a group of AIA rats gavaged with L. casei ( n = 7), a group of AIA rats gavaged with MTX ( n = 7), a group of AIA rats gavaged with GJK ( n = 7) or ZQFNT ( n = 7), and a group of AIA rats fed a high - fat diet ( D12492) ( n = 7).
